true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "5e79233", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width:820px\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Local Focus</span>\n<h2>Built for the pace of a London bridal boutique</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p>From Mayfair to Shoreditch, London's bridal boutiques are busy, appointment-led and fiercely competitive. When your phone rings during a fitting, a missed call can mean a lost consultation. Ivory Digital gives your shop its own booking website so brides can reserve a slot themselves, day or night, without anyone lifting the phone.</p>\n<p>Behind the scenes you get a calm, single diary that shows every consultant, every fitting room and every location at a glance \u2014 so two brides can never land on the same slot, even during a packed Saturday in the capital.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "ec16403", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "96ca02f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">The Local Advantage</span>\n<h2>Why London boutiques choose Ivory Digital</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Owned by you</h3><p>Your system is private and branded to your shop, not a shared London directory that charges you for every booking.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Fewer no-shows</h3><p>Automatic confirmations and reminders keep busy London brides on track, cutting empty appointment slots.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Ready for multiple stores</h3><p>Running boutiques across several boroughs? Manage them all from one tidy dashboard.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "b663aee", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "314a21f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Your Brand, Front and Centre</span>\n<h2>A London boutique deserves a London-boutique brand</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">Your booking page carries your name, your colours and your photography \u2014 never ours. Brides move from your Instagram to your booking page without ever feeling handed off to a third party.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 3l9 9-9 9-9-9z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2.4\"></circle></svg><h3>Your logo &amp; colours</h3><p>We style the whole booking journey in your boutique's colours and drop in your logo, so it looks like a natural part of your own website.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">