ly free slots.</p></details>\n<details><summary>Is it really branded to my boutique?</summary><p>Yes \u2014 your logo, colours, photos and even your own web address. Brides see your brand from start to finish.</p></details>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "af563d1", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "f0959e4", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"cta-band\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">London Bridal Boutiques</span>\n<h2>Give your London boutique its own booking system.</h2>\n<p>Start a free 7-day trial and see your brand, your diary and your booking page come together.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"justify-content:center\"><a class=\"btn btn-light\" href=\"/contact/\">Start Your Free 7-Day Trial</a></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "31b06ac", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "bc9274e", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n<div class=\"container footer-grid\">\n<div class=\"footer-brand\"><img alt=\"Ivory Digital\" class=\"footer-logo\" src=\"__IVORY_BASE__/assets/img/logo